{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Recognise period pants as a menstrual product so that they can be taxed fairly",
        "additional_details": "This creates an unfair playing field for disposable period products to be lower price than sustainable period pants taxed at 20% VAT.\r\n\r\nWe need your support. Sustainable periods are not a luxury!\r\n\r\nWe would like ministers to simply address this inequality and make Period Pants 0% VAT along with disposable menstrual products in the new financial year.",
        "background": "The Government announced there will be no period tax on women\u2019s sanitary products from Jan 2021 but has failed to acknowledge reusable period pants as a menstrual product.",
